    "steam_appid": 2164500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/19545e929d3accfcf45a34586361146d.poster.avif?t=1771824552\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/19545e929d3accfcf45a34586361146d.webm?t=1771824552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/19545e929d3accfcf45a34586361146d.mp4?t=1771824552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《99 Fails》是一款几乎不可能通关的单键 Roguelite 平台动作游戏，舞台设在 Zeebo 超现实的噩梦之中，充满怪诞的怪物，并由传奇作曲家 David Wise 倾情配乐。玩法前提非常简单：操控处于不同形态的 Zeebo 踏过一根根立柱，而怪诞的环境则竭尽全力分散你的注意力！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在单键立柱跳跃中检验你的技术，通过三种不同机制前进。随着立柱的距离、位置和可见度发生变化，操作将变得越来越刁钻。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与注意力作战。Zeebo 的大脑会用各种超现实的精神事件来干扰你：时间忽快忽慢，视野镜像翻转，诡异的幻想怪物在画面中晃动、追逐你，甚至想把你从节奏中“戳”下去。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色彩鲜艳的手绘 2D 画面，逐渐显露出怪诞、阴森甚至有些怪诡的一面，许多玩家形容它为<i>“超现实、漂亮、却令人不安”。</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欣赏由《Donkey Kong Country》名作曲家、传奇人物 David Wise 创作的劲爆主配乐！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/9c4fb215402b31f94c2409736833232a.avif?t=1771824552\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/c4ec811a457122fa4a054c00b7d1c132.webp?t=1771824552\" width=600 height=20 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一张张地图上穿过精心制作的关卡片段和检查点，一边推进，一边解锁 Zeebo 所在世界 Neebota 的更多秘密。通过一幅幅精美手绘的漫画分镜，拼出他悲伤的身世故事。通关游戏即可解锁全部页面！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/a0b556c52a4a194245df52d3091d61dc.avif?t=1771824552\" width=600 height=386 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/e7f2f4037845105d614c34e8f89d0714.avif?t=1771824552\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在街机模式中，你可以在三种难度下挑战自己，穿越 99 或 666 根程序生成的立柱，游历不同区域，还可以和好友与对手一起同场竞技。最多 4 名玩家同时起跑，看看谁先冲到终点！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/e76eb3c98c03dbed259ab6cead67e0a5.poster.avif?t=1771824552\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/e76eb3c98c03dbed259ab6cead67e0a5.webm?t=1771824552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/e76eb3c98c03dbed259ab6cead67e0a5.mp4?t=1771824552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/32436617d758db68a7a63a229c89bb9a.avif?t=1771824552\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你究竟能走多远？其他人又能走多远？无尽模式始终保持在线，全世界的玩家同时竞争，看谁能跑得最远。最终只能有一位真正的第一名！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/57f679ab1eab4b23494a0456b5e6559f.poster.avif?t=1771824552\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/57f679ab1eab4b23494a0456b5e6559f.webm?t=1771824552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/57f679ab1eab4b23494a0456b5e6559f.mp4?t=1771824552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/0b22b2b7dce237b2308651dd6ae53867.avif?t=1771824552\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Neebota</strong> 是一个全新的奇幻宇宙，这里的一切存在都在与希望、恐惧、梦想和自我认知搏斗。它的梦境世界 <strong>Noobota</strong> 映照着居民的内心：扭曲、美丽，又层层叠叠充满含义。Zeebo、Laurencia、Rashkadim 和 Bervie 是一群好友，他们在 Neebota 中寻找通往我们地球的传送门，同时在噩梦中直面真正的自己。<br><br><strong>99 Fails</strong> 是 Zeebo 梦境中的一个片段，由独立工作室 <strong>Frying Jelly</strong> 开发。工作室专注于打造原创 IP 和能让人沉浸其中的世界，而宏大的 RPG《Neebota: Zeebo's Awakening》正是他们始终努力实现的梦想之作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢你支持我们，这对我们意义重大！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/3bc83498db9afb1acd12364bc5efe530.poster.avif?t=1771824552\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164500/extras/3bc83498db9afb1acd12364bc5efe530.webm?t=1771824552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
